/*
--------------------------------------
VEERG_4_5_1_3__7_NitrogenTransferredToStage2MMS
Nitrogen transferred to treatment stage 2 MMS
NT_jmT2
kg N
NT_{jm,T=2}=MN_{jm,T=1}\times(1-FracGASM_{m,T=1}-EF_{m,T=1})
MN_jmT1 = nitrogen per swine class in treatment stage 1 MMS (kg N)
FracGASMmT1 = fraction of N volatilised from MMS treatment at stage 1
EF_mT1 = nitrous oxide emission factor for MMS treatment at stage 1
--------------------------------------
